about theatrical photography first.

553
00:31:51,476 --> 00:31:53,944
Hey, fella, don't get high hat on me.
This is America.

554
00:31:54,045 --> 00:31:56,513
- You are what you say you are.
- Well...

555
00:31:56,614 --> 00:32:00,607
