571
00:32:57,342 --> 00:33:00,209
What did Joanna take with her
when she ran out on you?

572
00:33:00,311 --> 00:33:02,711
Joanna... All right.
At least hold on to your keys.

573
00:33:02,814 --> 00:33:05,806
