for random manipulation...

623
00:35:46,677 --> 00:35:48,872
and tawdry circulation!

624
00:35:48,980 --> 00:35:53,076
<i>In other words,
there is no open season on my words.!</i>

625
00:35:53,184 --> 00:35:56,676
<i>Not any longer!</i>

626
00:36:03,361 --> 00:36:06,660
