on her part...

1424
01:19:42,417 --> 01:19:45,875
could make up for
the lack of wardrobe on mine.

1425
01:19:45,987 --> 01:19:48,888
<i>Told me the first time
she saw me walk into the library...</i>

1426
01:19:48,990 --> 01:19:52,153
<i>she thought I might be a bag man
coming in from the weather.</i>

1427
01:19:52,260 --> 01:19:57,493
