1491
01:23:36,551 --> 01:23:39,315
<i>it's gonna waste me, Jake.!</i>

1492
01:23:39,420 --> 01:23:41,684
<i>It is gonna kill me.</i>

1493
01:23:41,789 --> 01:23:46,158
