1512
01:24:59,233 --> 01:25:02,691
And if that's the case, Jake,
and I think it is...

1513
01:25:04,405 --> 01:25:06,373
then I understand.

1514
01:25:07,675 --> 01:25:09,643
I sympathize.

1515
01:25:11,245 --> 01:25:13,213
I empathize with you.

1516
01:25:14,582 --> 01:25:18,143
