or withdraw it.

1518
01:25:25,293 --> 01:25:28,854
How could I do a thing like that
if it meant hurting the book?

1519
01:25:28,963 --> 01:25:30,931
<i>Would you?</i>

1520
01:25:33,267 --> 01:25:35,132
Would you?

1521
01:25:38,773 --> 01:25:43,176
