1522
01:25:43,277 --> 01:25:46,371
or to hurt you, to use you, ever.

1523
01:25:46,481 --> 01:25:48,449
I mean, that's a given.

1524
01:25:51,419 --> 01:25:53,751
I just...

1525
01:25:53,855 --> 01:25:57,814
